    "en": {
      "title": "One person was killed in a shooting in Bemmulla",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Police say that a person has died in a shooting in the Bandarabatawala area under the Bemmulla police jurisdiction.",
        "The police say that the killing took place at around five in the morning today (4) and a 41-year-old man named Joseph Kumara, a resident of Elpitiya area, has died.",
        "The deceased is said to be an underworld member and the body has been taken to Gampaha Hospital."
      ],
